      "name": "Primary hemolysis validation — FDA pump PIV and hemolysis bench comparison",
      "description": "CFD predictions of normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against bench-top hemolysis measurements at 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error 12.3%. This result was generated by the ansys-cfx-2024q3-build-2 solver configuration, which corresponds to modelVersion 2024-q3-build-2. The UnitOfAssurance currentModelVersion is 2026-q1-build-7. The solver was subsequently updated with revised turbulence wall-treatment coefficients and an updated hemolysis power-law exponent in the 2025-q2 and 2026-q1 releases; the validation evidence predates those changes and no re-validation run has been performed.",
